This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on analyzing neural language models. The paper also uses techniques from machine learning and cognitive neuroscience, which makes it likely to also belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions using fMRI brain imaging data, which suggests it could also belong to the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision) as this sub-category often deals with image analysis and processing.
